  "text": "The contact force can then be determined by multiplying the stiffness matrix of the beam by the deflection calculated from the tip support. Fig. 3 compares the contact forces calculated by the DQM with the values predicted by the hybrid BEM and FEM approach [CITATION_1] . The two sets of results are similar and mutually consistent.",
